      <hr />
      <h3>FIELD DEFINITION AND SCOPE</h3>
      <div class="definition">
         <div>
            <p>Technical specifications relating to the projection of a moving image resource.</p>
         </div>
      </div>
      <hr />
      <h3>GUIDELINES FOR APPLYING CONTENT DESIGNATORS</h3>
      <div class="guidelines">
         <div>
            <p></p>
         </div>
         <h4><span class="box">â </span> INDICATORS
         </h4>
         <div class="indicators">
            <ul>
               <li>Both indicator positions are undefined; each contains a blank (#).</li>
            </ul>
         </div>
         <h4><span class="box">â </span> SUBFIELD CODES
         </h4>
         <div class="subfields">
            <div class="subfield">
               <div>
                  <p class="label"><strong>$a - Presentation format</strong> 
                  </p>
                  <div>
                     <p>The format used in the production of a projected image (e.g., Cinerama, IMAX).</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="example">
                     <table>
                        <tr>
                           <td><strong>345</strong></td>
                           <td colspan="9"><strong>##</strong><strong>$a</strong>3D<strong>$b</strong>48 fps<strong>$2</strong>rda
                           </td>
                        </tr>
                     </table>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="subfield">
               <div>
                  <p class="label"><strong>$b - Projection speed</strong> 
                  </p>
                  <div>
                     <p>The speed at which a projection device must be operated to produce the moving image intended.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="example">
                     <table>
                        <tr>
                           <td><strong>345</strong></td>
                           <td colspan="9"><strong>##</strong><strong>$a</strong>Cinerama<strong>$b</strong>24 fps<strong>$2</strong>rda
                           </td>
                        </tr>
                     </table>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="subfield">
               <div>
                  <p class="label"><strong>$0 - Authority record control number or standard number</strong> 
                  </p>
                  <div>
                     <p>See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control Subfields</a></em>.
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="subfield">
               <div>
                  <p class="label"><strong>$2 - Source</strong> 
                  </p>
                  <div>
                     <p>Identification of the source of terms when they are from a controlled list.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="subfield">
               <div>
                  <p class="label"><strong>$3 - Materials specified</strong> 
                  </p>
                  <div>
                     <p>Part of the described materials to which the field applies.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="subfield">
               <div>
                  <p class="label"><strong>$6 - Linkage</strong> 
                  </p>
                  <div>
                     <p>See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control Subfields</a></em>.
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="subfield">
               <div>
                  <p class="label"><strong>$8 - Field link and sequence number</strong> 
                  </p>
                  <div>
                     <p>See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control Subfields</a></em>.
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
